Package common.message

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IInstallCmdData
    This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the install new command command (command that has a new a command), which is an ADataPacketAlgoCmd, that notifies its receiver that it has a command for an originally unknown type for the sender.
    IJoinData
    This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the join team command, which is an ADataPacketAlgoCmd, that notifies its receiver that it wants to join a team.
    ILeaveData
    This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the leave team command, which is an ADataPacketAlgoCmd, that notifies its receiver that it wants to leave a team.
    IRequestCmdData
    This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the request new command command (command that gets a command), which is an ADataPacketAlgoCmd, that notifies its receiver that it needs a command for some unknown type.
    ITextData
    This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the send text team command, which is an ADataPacketAlgoCmd, that sends a text message to its receiver.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AMessageCmd<T extends IDataPacketData>
    /** An abstract class that all commands should extend.
    GroupDataPacket<T extends IDataPacketData>
    These are the type-narrowed data packets that are sent as messages.
    GroupDataPacketAlgo
    The visitor that processes team data packets.
